WEBVTT

00:00:00.990 --> 00:00:02.539
Zdravo, deco.

00:00:02.539 --> 00:00:04.099
(Smeh)

00:00:04.099 --> 00:00:06.683
Imam 71 godinu.

00:00:06.683 --> 00:00:08.778
(Aplauz)

00:00:08.778 --> 00:00:11.580
Moj muž ima 76 godina.

00:00:11.580 --> 00:00:15.040
Moji roditelji su u kasnim 90-im,

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:17.730
a Olivija, pas, ima 16 godina.

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:19.690
Hajde da pričamo o starenju.

00:00:19.690 --> 00:00:21.968
Dozvolite da vam ispričam kako se osećam

00:00:21.968 --> 00:00:23.875
kada vidim svoje bore u ogledalu

00:00:23.875 --> 00:00:27.200
i shvatim
da su se neki delovi mene opustili

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:29.832
i ne mogu ih naći tamo dole.

00:00:29.832 --> 00:00:30.970
(Smeh)